  "title": "Legal Counsel - EH03",
  "description": "<p><strong>Legal Counsel</strong></p><ul><li>Location: Boon Lay</li><li>Working Days: Monday- Friday, 5 days</li><li>Working hours: 8am to 530pm</li><li>Salary :  ($5,500 7,000) Open to Negotiation </li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Draft, review and negotiate contracts, agreements and other documents; and render legal advice</li><li>Provide legal advice and support to the group of companies on a broad range of commercial issues</li><li>Handle the setting up of subsidiaries, associates, branches and project offices as well as the closing or liquidation of such set up</li><li>Coordinate with external legal counsels and consultants as well as oversee the progress of their work</li><li>Coordinate with and advise business units and departments on legal matters</li><li>Any other duties to be assigned from time to time</li></ul><p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Law</li><li>4 to 7 years’ post-qualification experience, with knowledge of construction law and/or with experience in the construction industry</li><li>Willing to travel when required</li></ul><p>✅Interested personnel kindly send your CV to WhatsApp: https://wa.me/65 88567364(Ethan)</p><p>Han Meng Zhuo | Reg No: R25138931</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</p><p></p>",
